vsParam:
Ah, that's Sterk! Is he training?
He's still so powerful and intimidating!

Hmm. He just trained with us this morning,
and now he's having additional training in private!
You should have a good rest...

Hey, you guys.
After all, my duty is to fight.

Uh, you guys.
No, I'm not done with my training.

Uh, I'm deeply touched by your will to protect your "partners".
I can't lose to you.

Hmm? But, you have done an excellent job
of protecting us, right?

Exactly, and we can feel your determination
to protect us!

No matter... no matter how firm my determination is,
I can't be a qualified knight if I'm weak.

I must keep improving my strength, so that I'll be able to
protect my people when I go back to my world.

A knight as powerful as you
is seeking greater power!?

Y-yes. Sterk is a knight of Arland.
He will go back to that world one day...

Uh... Please don't get upset about this. As long as I'm here,
I'll protect the "partners" in the Academy...

And I'll protect you guys who are protecting those
"partners". I swear to this sword as a knight.

Hee hee!
Er, it's so reassuring to hear that, Sterk!
